  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>Specially conditioned oil is added to the jetpack's exhaust jets, creating a stream of pearlescent bubbles as it operates.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观</span>。<br><br>喷气背包排出的废气中添加了一种特殊油脂，启动之后就能在身后留下一串带有珍珠光泽的泡泡。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>中调整你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>將特殊保養油塗抹在噴射背包的噴射口，使其在運作時產生珍珠光澤的泡泡尾跡。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>裡改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
  },
